snippet.title: The Sims 4 City Living: Official Neighborhoods Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to San Myshuno! Explore the city’s unique neighborhoods, each with their own charm and personality.

Paint graffiti in the up and coming Spice Market, show off your style in the trendy Fashion District, visit a museum in the bohemian Arts Quarter, or fight for a cause in the upscale Uptown. Need an escape?  Get back to nature in Myshuno Meadows. Check out San Myshuno today!

Learn more about this Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/16994
